title: Pantera - (1997) - Official Live 101 Proof [320kbs] ~~Renovatio~
description:
Official Live: 101 Proof is a live album released by Pantera on July 29, 1997. The first fourteen tracks are live recordings of songs from previously released studio albums (starting with Cowboys from Hell); the last two songs ("Where You Come from" and "I Can't Hide") are new studio recordings.
